{"id":154,"parent_id":141,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":154,"title":"1 Corinthians 13","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 13"],[".studySummary",["i","Paul discusses the high status of charity—Charity, a pure love, excels and exceeds almost all else."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.1","order":"03.09.013.17905"},["b","1"],"Though I speak with the tongues of men and of angels, and have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"charity"],", I am become",["i","as"],"sounding brass, or a tinkling cymbal."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.2","order":"03.09.013.17906"},["b","2"],"And though I have",["i","the gift of"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"prophecy"],", and understand all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"mysteries"],", and all knowledge; and though I have all faith, so that I could remove mountains, and have not charity, I am nothing."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.3","order":"03.09.013.17907"},["b","3"],"And though I bestow all my goods to feed",["i","the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"poor"],","],"and though I give my body to be burned, and have not charity, it profiteth me nothing."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.4","order":"03.09.013.17908"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Charity"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"suffereth"],"long,",["i","and"],"is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"kind"],"; charity",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"envieth"],"not; charity vaunteth not itself, is not puffed up,"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.5","order":"03.09.013.17909"},["b","5"],"Doth not behave itself",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"unseemly"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"seeketh not"],"her own, is not easily",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"provoked"],", thinketh no evil;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.6","order":"03.09.013.17910"},["b","6"],"Rejoiceth not in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"iniquity"],", but rejoiceth in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"truth"],";"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.7","order":"03.09.013.17911"},["b","7"],"Beareth all things, believeth all things, hopeth all things, endureth all things."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.8","order":"03.09.013.17912"},["b","8"],"Charity never",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"faileth"],": but whether",["i","there be"],"prophecies, they shall fail; whether",["i","there be"],"tongues, they shall cease; whether",["i","there be"],"knowledge, it shall vanish away."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.9","order":"03.09.013.17913"},["b","9"],"For we know in part, and we prophesy in part."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.10","order":"03.09.013.17914"},["b","10"],"But when that which is perfect is come, then that which is in part shall be done away."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.11","order":"03.09.013.17915"},["b","11"],"When I was a child, I spake as a child, I understood as a child, I thought as a child: but when I became a man, I put away childish things."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.12","order":"03.09.013.17916"},["b","12"],"For now we see through a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"glass"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"darkly"],"; but then face to face: now I know in part; but then shall I know even as also I am known."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.13","order":"03.09.013.17917"},["b","13"],"And now abideth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"faith"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"hope"],",",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"charity"],", these three; but the greatest of these",["i","is"],"charity."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.1a","order":"03.09.013.17918"},["b","1a"],["span.small","GR"],"love."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.2a","order":"03.09.013.17920"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophecy"},"TG Prophecy"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.2b","order":"03.09.013.17922"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mysteries-of-godliness"},"TG Mysteries of Godliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.3a","order":"03.09.013.17924"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/welfare"},"TG Welfare"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.4a","order":"03.09.013.17926"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/charity"},"TG Charity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courtesy"},"Courtesy"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.4b","order":"03.09.013.17928"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forbear"},"TG Forbear"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.4c","order":"03.09.013.17930"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/benevolence"},"TG Benevolence"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.4d","order":"03.09.013.17932"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/envy"},"TG Envy"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.5a","order":"03.09.013.17934"},["b","5a"],["span.small","GR"],"indecently, unbecomingly."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.5b","order":"03.09.013.17936"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/selfishness"},"TG Selfishness"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.5c","order":"03.09.013.17938"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/anger"},"TG Anger"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/provoking"},"Provoking"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-mastery"},"Self-Mastery"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.6a","order":"03.09.013.17940"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"injustice, unrighteousness."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.6b","order":"03.09.013.17942"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/truth"},"TG Truth"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.8a","order":"03.09.013.17944"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dependability"},"TG Dependability"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.12a","order":"03.09.013.17946"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.18"},"2 Cor. 3:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/1.23.22-27"},"James 1:23 (22–27)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/veil"},"TG Veil"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.12b","order":"03.09.013.17948"},["b","12b"],["span.small","GR"],"obscurely, enigmatically."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.13a","order":"03.09.013.17950"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.13b","order":"03.09.013.17952"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hope"},"TG Hope"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.13c","order":"03.09.013.17954"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"TG Love"],"."]]}
